<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUS IS MINE!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel hi bei mahleh,
 Isu kei a;
 Thildang cheng sang inle,
 Ka deih pen hi.
 Khawvel gitloh thim ah,
 Lungmuonna la umlo;
 Isu maiin a nei,
 Isu kei a.

[V2]
 2. Ka thagau manglo in,
 Isu zui in;
 Kumsawt chanin Ama'n hun pui ina,
 Dahum hungtun laiin,
 Lungmuonna hun pie'na;
 Lungngai in um puon la,
 Isu zui in.

[V3]
 3. Zan hung tung mahlele,
 Isu ka nei;
 Keidi'n khuo vak ina,
 Isu vakin.
 Ka thagau damna chuh,
 Amah kiengah a um;
 A thisan in ei chawi,
 Isu kei a.

[V4]
 4. Thihna ka chan tieng leh,
 Isu'n ei zui;
 Ama'n ei pui ina,
 Van gam tiengin.
 Gam nuom ka tun tieng leh,
 Kumsawt in chawl ing ka;
 Amah chuh kumsawt in,
 Chawi-an ing ka.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>83</hymn_number>
</song>